videos.description: Kansas using some great passing and ball movement and it leads to a Josh Jackson 3 pointer.
videos.headline: Great ball movement by Kansas leads to Jackson 3-pointer

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte Graham finds Josh Jackson with the lob pass to beat the zone for the Jayhawks.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson hammers home the alley-oop

videos.description: Frank Mason cant finish the layup but Josh Jackson cleans it up and slams it home on the put back dunk.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson hammers home the put back dunk

videos.description: Texas Tech's Justin Gray gets the steal and it leads to a Niem Stevenson dunk over the Kansas defender.
videos.headline: Texas Tech gets the steal leads to Stevenson dunk

videos.description: Josh Jackson throws the deep pass to Devonte Graham who passes to Legerald Vick who dunks over the Texas Tech defender.
videos.headline: Jackson's football pass leads to Vick dunk

videos.description: Josh Jackson hits free to give Kansas the lead and Texas Tech misses the final shot from half court to give Jayhawks the victory.
videos.headline: Josh Jackson free throw clinches win for Kansas
